---
// Import content from migration
const content = await import('../../migration_static/content/extracted_content.json');
const company = content.default.company;
---

<section id="philosophy" class="section-padding bg-gray-900 text-white" aria-labelledby="philosophy-heading">
  <div class="container-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 id="philosophy-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          Our Philosophy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We're not building tools that think for people. 
          We're building tools that help people think better.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Core Philosophy -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary-300 mb-8">
          "{company.philosophy}"
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
          This isn't about making things simpler. It's about making complexity navigable. 
          The nuance remains—we just help you find what matters for your decision.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Philosophy Principles -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Translation, Not Simplification</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                We don't dumb down the world. We make it comprehensible. 
                The complexity stays available for those who want to dig deeper.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Agency Restoration</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Every feature should increase user control, not decrease it. 
                We augment human judgment, never replace it.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Performance as Trust</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Sub-second load times aren't a technical metric—they're trust building. 
                Speed demonstrates our ability to manage complexity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9v-9m0-9v9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Accessibility as Right</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Cognitive augmentation must be universally accessible. 
                Just as glasses restore vision, our tools restore choice.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- The Vision -->
      <div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-900 to-primary-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Building Cognitive Infrastructure for the Next Century
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We're at an inflection point. AI can now translate any complexity into human understanding. 
          The question isn't whether this will happen—it's who will do it right.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-300 mb-2">Today</div>
            <div class="text-primary-100">Food and money decisions</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-300 mb-2">Tomorrow</div>
            <div class="text-primary-100">Every complex choice</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-300 mb-2">Future</div>
            <div class="text-primary-100">Thinking clearly again</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- The Test -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">The Ultimate Test</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Does using our website feel like having a "trusted companion for thought"? 
          If you experience that here, you'll understand what our apps can do for your daily decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>